

1️⃣ What is React?

● React: One of the most popular JavaScript libraries                                     Djy  yyjj   
to build SPA (Single Page Application)                                                    D   z8   E   
  ■ Popular alternatives: Angular, VueJS                                                 z8y8w zByZw  
● Open-source project created by Facebook                                               9  D5 Dz jz  Bw
